  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. This package is submitted under ProfileMinimal. All 13 credibility factors are recorded and a decision record is present. No context of use is bound to this unit of assurance; the intended-use scope is therefore undefined in this package.",
